asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Ride-Machete-Snowboard-2013/280966P,default,pd.html?dwvar_280966P_SwatchValue=152cm  You will be making slash after slash all over the mountain with the Ride Machete. The Machete features Rides LowRize rocker shape which will eliminate hook and makes this deck super easy to use. The Pop Rods 1.0 Core gives the board an extra dose of pop to help turn that 360 into a 540 and a landing so smooth you will think you were landing on a cloud. Couple that with smooth riding slimewalls and durable Cleave Edge for a fun surfy twin that will let you rock out with your pop out.
